translate ru NeitherPath7_e2d2ef63:
    # "Sarah watches as the many invited guests flow into the great hall."
    ""

translate ru NeitherPath7_12d885c9:
    # "The annual celebration of Rosanna's unity is underway. Officially meant to celebrate the many ways in which the nation was thriving, in truth, a reminder of how Sarah had brought low the usurpers."
    ""

translate ru NeitherPath7_afe5c734:
    # "She smiled and greeted the throng of newcomers."
    ""

translate ru NeitherPath7_522c5cbf:
    # "On the far side of the room, Varga was chatting with a group of nobles."
    ""

translate ru NeitherPath7_c23dd2f4:
    # "Sarah could only laugh whenever she watched Varga try to play his part."
    ""

translate ru NeitherPath7_7884c4da:
    # "The years had made him more talented at pretending, but she had long accepted that her warmaster would never truly be a creature of the court."
    ""

translate ru NeitherPath7_6991b3d4:
    # "She was happy for that fact."
    ""

translate ru NeitherPath7_9451ff8a:
    # "The crowd had changed over the years."
    ""

translate ru NeitherPath7_11efc6b5:
    # "Nobles still made up a large share of those in attendance, but each passing year the crowd grew more diverse. Sucessful merchants, famous scholars, notable guests from across the world."
    ""

translate ru NeitherPath7_a363a36e:
    # "Rosanna had become somewhat of a hub for all those who sought to make their luck for themselves."
    ""

translate ru NeitherPath7_44ab001c:
    # "Sarah was glad for it, if only because the new crowd seemed less obsessed with protocol."
    ""

translate ru NeitherPath7_90d8adf6:
    # "Still, no royal court could ever truly escape it, and so Sarah continued to play her part."
    ""

translate ru NeitherPath7_45aba37a:
    # "Each guest bore with them a gift, and soon the many gifts began to pile up next to her. The pile grew so large that it soon became embarassing."
    ""

translate ru NeitherPath7_18b8d0db:
    # "With a small gesture of a hand, Sarah instructed the servants to begin carrying the gifts away for storage."
    ""

